{"tid":1847771,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"大家原唔原諒金希澈??","createTime":"2020-01-28T07:54:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T11:16:29.000Z","uid":74065,"like":4,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c6e5d5df060264409b5ccfe538149ec30b03270b","tid":1847771,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:54:57.000Z","msg":"南韓人氣團體Super Junior成員金希澈出道15年，2019年底首度承認與女團TWICE成員Momo的戀情，他出道以來形象良好、對粉絲誠實，此次公開戀情，也受到很多人的祝福，然而，他卻因此陷入愧疚感，28日出演太妍固定節目《Petionista Taengoo》，首度談到這段期間的心聲，承認「我反而內疚了」，令歌迷不捨。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4671/d4671452.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4671%2Fd4671452.jpg&h=e0ff2fb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲金希澈認愛後，首吐心聲看到粉絲的支持，反而讓他內疚了。（圖／翻攝自Vlive）<br />\n<br />\n金希澈認愛Momo，但網路有傳聞兩人早就交往2、3年，對此，他感到無奈，首度在節目裡正式回應「那都不是真的，那時候我們根本還不熟。」而他也對於粉絲願意繼續支持、應援感到感謝，心想著「看來我這15年還是不錯的」，不過，另一方面，他也開始有了內疚感，「就算粉絲可能感到傷心，但還是會說沒關係，我們哥哥一直以來都沒有出什麼大事，會應援哥哥、支持哥哥，這樣的心情，反而讓我覺得很愧疚。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4671/d4671450.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4671%2Fd4671450.jpg&h=a2da28c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼金希澈向太妍吐心聲，「我好像沒本事當藝人」。（圖／翻攝自Vlive）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4671/d4671453.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4671%2Fd4671453.jpg&h=2c552f26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n金希澈形容，粉絲給予的愛太多、與預期還多，他若把所有的愛都收下，反而會感到抱歉，因此腦海閃過「我沒本事當藝人」的念頭，不過，與他情如親兄妹的太妍安慰「只有哥哥這樣瘋子才適合當藝人啊，不然誰能做？」他立刻笑出來回應「你這是安慰還是諷刺啊？」面對妹妹太妍的開導，他才露出笑容。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4671/d4671449.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4671%2Fd4671449.jpg&h=aaee27ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲金希澈、太妍情如親兄妹。（圖／翻攝自Vlive）<br />\n<br />\n事實上，太妍與金希澈都是重視粉絲意見的偶像，因此也很遵守與歌迷的約定，對此，太妍開口坦言「這份責任感我真的想要守約」，金希澈也回應「雖然妳是妹妹，但看到妳這樣，我真的很尊敬妳，雖然性格真的很差，但我很尊敬妳。」正是因為重視粉絲，才會有愧疚感。節目播出後，歌迷也紛紛表示「希望哥哥不要內疚」。"},{"pid":"f06bf4509513f242fd882cda16fd9cd4843142f7","tid":1847771,"uid":136738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:55:43.000Z","msg":"當然是選擇原諒他"},{"pid":"e8517bcd0af495b1d485f1221f7117c7f64c1b35","tid":1847771,"uid":132174,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:56:27.000Z","msg":"問緊once?"},{"pid":"f063181b83b1fd87a1863f2f8fbffcf19e7a7767","tid":1847771,"uid":256952,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:58:00.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"b3821d56eba9c5f80853d9b5e20d6e25beaef5a9","tid":1847771,"uid":210165,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:58:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9bb4db200a0aee5a654dd3aa6ae1f7f68ac8aa5b","tid":1847771,"uid":143093,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T08:02:04.000Z","msg":"屌你老母拎住光環實原諒你架"},{"pid":"a2dfb9864cc9692c5be7481030d46b00fbd6bd11","tid":1847771,"uid":76115,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T08:14:48.000Z","msg":"無嬲過佢 低b妹隨便屌"},{"pid":"75e2639483d854ff890cab075ec89d85724230b4","tid":1847771,"uid":18196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T08:20:37.000Z","msg":"太妍希澈有冇扑過野？"},{"pid":"77d57d89d1caed843dacf8c547ec21de0684454b","tid":1847771,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75e2639483d854ff890cab075ec89d85724230b4","tid":1847771,"uid":18196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T08:20:37.000Z","msg":"太妍希澈有冇扑過野？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T08:33:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abcaeaeb2ee83f050e3897a7b214707fbecdaf27","tid":1847771,"uid":135742,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T08:38:43.000Z","msg":"會原諒希澈哥哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a076487dbef47021f9228c608c5b177c66bbc3a2","tid":1847771,"uid":88491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T08:39:52.000Z","msg":"唔原諒金泰妍"},{"pid":"d990e25dd0a64ed6763cf5cac3d5a41217253f68","tid":1847771,"uid":2781,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:02:36.000Z","msg":"佢做錯乜嘢"},{"pid":"d961852370450007fd812db12c16282ac546ab14","tid":1847771,"uid":46435,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:06:17.000Z","msg":"希澈老師無做錯到!!!!!!"},{"pid":"22b6fb7d4360a772a487129ba68b360ff6fc3e72","tid":1847771,"uid":149371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T10:36:08.000Z","msg":"無錯點原諒🙄"},{"pid":"9ee7ca6eb41aa3ff6cf0c32e237f1dce3d7a4aba","tid":1847771,"uid":165339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T10:37:09.000Z","msg":"拍拖都唔撚比？"},{"pid":"1ee5be55f3bea56c278adc0c69a94be7e93beee2","tid":1847771,"uid":323791,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T11:16:29.000Z","msg":"冇嬲過 btw太妍個樣怪怪的"}]}